column5: A new coach...... Some hot new rookies..... Subban with a 2 year contract.... With tonite 10-4-1...... A great player mesh........  things are going good in this shortened season.
Not a Habs fan by a long shot, (Leafs baby) but there doin it some how this year. I think sometime yesterday they were 2nd in the East....far cry from last years finish.
Glad you started a Habs thread!!!  And they are looking pretty good!!!
Go Leafs go , but ya Habs are looking good..Still wont beat our beloved Leafs....
Go Leafs Go but ya they look pretty good. I'm hoping for good years from the Leafs and Habs
Leafs looking better........
Hope Gallager is back soon.  Vive Les Habitants!
I've been a Habs fan all my life and it's great to see they're doing good. I have a lot of friends who are Maple Leaf fans so I'm happy for them as well.
OLE OLE OLE OLE OLE!!!!
